idate that with minimal content. \\n\\nSpeaking of the XML block, I have to check if there's an issue with the leading newline and ensure the string formatting is correct. It looks like there might be some nuances there!\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Assessing potential issues and features**\\n\\nOkay, I see that in the source, there’s only one attribute line, which is good. But I have a potential issue with `fromFile(String)` in the native image since it might read from the temp filesystem instead of resources. I also noted that `Files.writeString` is available in Java 11 and JDK 21. \\n\\nI need to check if the \\\"default protocol and extension\\\" are included. It seems like testing the import from a standard XML file path with namespace could be more of a functional library feature. Time to summarize this concisely!\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented the new test in:\n\n`tests/src/org.jboss.arquillian.config/arquillian-config-api/1.1.10.Final/src/test/java/org_jboss_arquillian_config/arquillian_config_api/Arquillian_config_apiTest.java`\n\nWhat was already covered:\n- Fluent descriptor construction for engine, default protocol, containers, protocols, groups, and extensions.\n- XML export/import roundtrip from `String`.\n- XML export/import roundtrip through streams.\n- Preservation of multiline and XML-escaped property values.\n- Modifying an imported descriptor and re-exporting it.\n\nNew feature covered:\n- Importing a user-authored `arquillian.xml` descriptor from a filesystem path via the public `Descriptors.importAs(...).fromFile(String)` API.\n\nAdded test:\n- `descriptorCanBeImportedFromXmlFilePath`\n  - Writes a standard namespaced Arquillian XML descriptor to a temporary file.\n  - Imports it through the file-path importer.\n  - Verifies descriptor name, engine properties, container metadata, and dependencies.\n\nI did not modify existing test logic or build files, and I did not run the tests.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c7c624b4be21fd70169fda77e7e3881929b9062144afd76fb\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3164, "output": 713, "cacheRead": 38912, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42789, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778231149665, "responseId": "resp_0c7c624b4be21fd70169fda76f18208192918a50b57bcbedd6"}, "toolResults": []}
